imagination_hand.name: Ticket To Cloud Rings
imagination_hand.desc: Activate this card to blast through all the cloud rings, collecting quoins as you go. Don't forget to enjoy the view a bit.

imagination_hand.name: Trade Channelling
imagination_hand.desc: Gives access to the "Trade Channel" a game-wide chat channel for buyers to find those selling the things they want to buy, and also the same thing but the other way around.

imagination_hand.name: Beginner Haggler
imagination_hand.desc: Get haggling! Vendor prices are lowered by 2%.

ezcooking_1.title: Breezy, EZ Cookin'
ezcooking_1.desc: Get started making delicious, nutritious foods!

offer_conversation.txt: So, you have an interest in cooking, huh? Well it may surprise you to know that every Master Chef starts by working with a Knife & Board. You ready to learn some cooking skills?

camera_abilities.skills_msg: With Eyeballery, you can move the camera around the whole location.
